Package scs1_group1.record

Class AppointmentOutcomeRecord

Object
Record
AppointmentOutcomeRecord
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Record
Represents an appointment outcome record, which contains information about the outcome of an appointment, including consultation notes, service type, and prescriptions.

      private void loadPrescriptions()
      Loads prescription details from a CSV file and adds them to the list of prescriptions. The prescriptions are filtered based on the appointment ID to match this instance.
